{
  "stem": "6989.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, she left me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She did not take me with her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She left me and hidden.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she went by herself to see whether she could bring me back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when she came back-- and see, nothing was really said directly to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's just that I hear-- heard these things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no one to bring me back to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In fact, you know, we had a Czech neighbor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know her name or anything, but this also Lena told me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she walked over to her and she said, you know-- because my mother said that if anything happened, she's going to leave some things with this Czech woman.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she came in and she asked her, she said, you know, I need some things from the household.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Czech woman said to her, leave right now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because if you don't, I'm going to say that you have a Jew with you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the only thing she gave her is like a spoon that I used to use.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, a soup spoon, which I have to this day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I don't know exactly where it is right now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But that's what Lena came home with.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well as I wanted to tell you, because they were afraid to keep me there, she had another sister by the name of Dunya that had a farm.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the Ukraine, they called it a [NON-ENGLISH], which means that it was a farm by itself not surrounded with other farms, very far from anything else.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was sort of all by itself with a lot of land.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had horses, cows.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember churning milk, and butter, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
